"post_flair_class": "", "id": 8639168, "raw_content": "I am no biologist and I cannot begin to tell you all of the intricacies of a cell but I do know that they have an incredibly complex arrangement; far more complex than anything designed by man and that every facet and part of that cell has to be arranged and placed in the right order in order for the organism to function properly.  If anything is out of place, misplaced, or even missing, it could either impair the function of the cell or even be fatal to the organism.\n\nHow could unthinking and unplanning and directionless random processes possibly be able to create something so incredibly complex and with all that is needed for it to function properly in the right arrangement?\n\nhttps://x.com/DivinelyDesined/status/2049180999519518801\n", "author": "ContendersEdge", "created": 1779723989427, "profile_picture": "OTUZVRkFHNZn", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Addicted2Clickbait", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "I am no biologist and I cannot begin to tell you all of the intricacies of a cell but I do know that they have an incredibly complex arrangement...\n", "last_comment_created": 1779730422042, "content": "<p>I am no biologist and I cannot begin to tell you all of the intricacies of a cell but I do know that they have an incredibly complex arrangement; far more complex than anything designed by man and that every facet and part of that cell has to be arranged and placed in the right order in order for the organism to function properly.  If anything is out of place, misplaced, or even missing, it could either impair the function of the cell or even be fatal to the organism.</p>\n<p>How could unthinking and unplanning and directionless random processes possibly be able to create something so incredibly complex and with all that is needed for it to function properly in the right arrangement?</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://x.com/DivinelyDesined/status/2049180999519518801\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/DivinelyDesined/status/2049180999519518801</a></p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 13, "score_up": 15, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2058882138720567406", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsZF0Yq1", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 28, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8638831, "raw_content": "", "author": "pepperonishoes", "created": 1779711731553, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "BrotherSeven", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsZF0Yq1.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/RepBrianMast/status/2058882138720567406", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Brian Mast (FL-Rep) shares an emotional remembrance about honoring his friends and everyone that made the ultimate sacrifice.", "last_comment_created": 1779721778802, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 28, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies":